<b>Opens up quest opportunities - </b>1/28/01 1:29:17 PM<br>~ <b>Kocho Divah</b><blockquote>I have played a variety of classes, and each one has certain quests that are open to them. As my bard, I try to do these quests, but sometimes my faction just ain't high enough. No worry, just a quick tune of this song is usually enough to let me perform the quest!<br><br>Of course, this also can get me slightly better prices when buying and selling. Not everything will be a better deal, but if you're selling a big item to a merchant, its worth a try to fire this song up. <br><br>This song will affect one faction group at a time, and affects the whole faction within the zone for about 15 minutes. Be sure not to use it behind a counter, you need a direct line to your merchant for the song to work.</blockquote></td></tr></table></blockquote><br><br><br><br>
